go.\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.462873003403436e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's greatest athletes\", \"from\": 3209, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"the backdrop\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"the most beautiful cities\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be the third time Paris has hosted the Olympics (1900 and 1924), tying London for the most as a Summer Games host.\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3412, \"end\": 3417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.462873003403436e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998777634648, \"rank\": 8.780368622985548e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third time\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"a Summer Games host\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles (1932, 1984) will tie those two cities when it hosts the first Summer Games in the U.S. in 32 years in 2028.\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3509, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999508872